'''''Hidden Treasures of Swat''''' ({{ISBN|978-969-23042-0-7}}) is a [[non-fiction]] book based on the achievements of Italian Archaeological Mission (IAM) in Pakistan and Department of [[Archaeology]] and Museums (DOAM) Pakistan.<ref name="Ministry of Information, Broadcasting & National Heritage, National Heritage & Integration Wing">{{cite web|title=Department of Archaeology and Museums (DOAM)|url=http://nationalheritage.gov.pk/doam.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315235152/http://nationalheritage.gov.pk/doam.html|archivedate=2015-03-15|df=}}</ref> Six major discoveries by Italian archaeologist in [[Swat District]] of [[Khyber Pukhtunkhwa]] Province of [[Pakistan]] have been discussed in the book.
